Avenger	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Specialization.SpecialQuality	DESC:Rushing from the shadows with a blade held high, the avenger vigilante uses skill at arms to strike down his foes. With an impressive array of combat-focused abilities, he can bring vengeance to those who have wronged him or his ideals.	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Avenger Vigilante ~ Class Skill|Avenger Vigilante ~ Assault Training																					DEFINE:Pool_Avenger_Vigilante_Talent|0	BONUS:VAR|Pool_Avenger_Vigilante_Talent|Vigilante_Talent_Count	
