Warlock	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Specialization.SpecialQuality	DESC:Practicing magic in secret, the warlock vigilante obscures his arcane scholarship from public view. His study of these arts allows him to hide his dual nature and enchant his enemies—or simply blast them with furious magical attacks.	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Warlock Vigilante ~ Class Skills|Warlock Vigilante ~ Arcane Training I|Warlock Vigilante ~ Spellbooks|Warlock Vigilante ~ Cantrips												DEFINE:Pool_Warlock_Vigilante_Talent|0	BONUS:VAR|Pool_Warlock_Vigilante_Talent|Vigilante_Talent_Count	
Zealot	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Specialization.SpecialQuality	DESC:Crusaders on a holy or unholy mission, zealot vigilantes often work for divine purpose in settlements in the need of grace or purging. Hiding their faith during the day, they work their divine will against the nonbelievers during the night from the shadows.	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Zealot Vigilante ~ Class Skill|Zealot Vigilante ~ Divine Training I|Zealot Vigilante ~ Orisons														DEFINE:Pool_Zealot_Vigilante_Talent|0	BONUS:VAR|Pool_Zealot_Vigilante_Talent|Vigilante_Talent_Count	

